{"tid":2073784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司、保安局、六紀律部隊首長發稿　全力支持配合國安法立法","createTime":"2020-06-21T14:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T16:33:27.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a324e270630fe76382db67bbea68b1c18676e7b9","tid":2073784,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】律政司、保安局及六個紀律部隊部門首長晚上分別發稿，指全力支持和配合國安法立法。<br />\n<br />\n新聞稿表示，保安局局長李家超連同警務處、海關、消防處、懲教署、入境處及飛行服務隊六個部門首長，全力支持中央制定國安法，李家超會帶領各紀律部隊全面履行應有職責，確保相關法律在香港有效實施，竭力維護國家安全，國安法草案提及警務處設立專職部門處理相關案件，保安局說會全面配合，籌備工作已經展開。　<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊就指，草案的說明清晰指出香港維護國家安全時，應當尊重和保障人權，並依照基本法和國際公約，保護香港居民享有的權利和自由，她認為可以釋除公眾的疑慮，將會率領律政司全力支持和配合國安法立法工作。"},{"pid":"e19c299e8c04e931572b41bec7e3f5519c4e7fe7","tid":2073784,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/28434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F28434&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=faa0d7da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F28434&h=72b15cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/28434</a>"},{"pid":"f85047b34d8be4128d4dc5bcdaeb83cff864cec2","tid":2073784,"uid":321854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cb92db9e6373cd885afba8054eaba3e60da776","tid":2073784,"uid":104138,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"我都支持呀，你唔通過我邊有 BNO !"},{"pid":"2e365e21781c2f517ef48494ff6560cd36d7ccc2","tid":2073784,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"草案的說明清晰指出香港維護國家安全時，應當尊重和保障人權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h